.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OPEN-DUAL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open-dual \- open a dual-funded channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open-dual
.I peer_id
.I our_sat
.I their_sat
.SH DESCRIPTION
Requests a dual-funded channel with
.IR peer_id ,
contributing
.I our_sat
satoshis from our side and requesting
.I their_sat
from the peer via
.BR fundchannel .
The peer must support dual funding (option_dual_fund).
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"channel_id":..., "txid":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-open (1),
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1)
